      • Builder

        public Builder(@NonNull
               android.content.Context context,
               @NonNull
               android.os.Bundle dataBundle,
               @NonNull
               DrmLicenseLoader.Callback callback)
        Create a new builder to generate a license loader instance using the given bundle data.

        The builder supports the following values specified in the bundle:

        • SdkConsts.INTENT_URL - (mandatory) The source URL to the content
        • SdkConsts.INTENT_DRM_CONFIGURATION - (mandatory) The DRM configuration
        • SdkConsts.INTENT_QUERY_PARAMS_BUNDLE - (optional) Bundle with additional query parameters
        • SdkConsts.INTENT_HEADER_PARAMS_BUNDLE - (optional) Bundle with additional header parameters
        • SdkConsts.INTENT_CONTENT_TYPE - (optional) Bundle with explicit content type
        • SdkConsts.INTENT_MERGE_VIDEO_TRACKS - (optional) Bundle with explicit merge video tracks flag
        Parameters:
        context - The context
        dataBundle - The bundle data
        callback - The callback
